"<blockquote><blockquote>CE = EE+CS<br />\n<br />\nCS = Computer Science<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分香港做緊既IT = Information System<br />\n<br />\n外國IT公司做緊既IT = CS/CE<br />\n<br />\n外國非IT公司做緊既IT = Information System</blockquote><br />\n咁即係香港做IT好搵啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然不是。<br />\n<br />\nInformation System (IS) 的地位，同一間公司中其他的 business function (Accounting, Finance, Operations Management, Human Resources Management) 的地位一樣，只係support business 的運作，點會好搵 ?"},{"pid":"87b2a3085758bdacadcb366f5351e8741d3bbb65","tid":474903,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T08:27:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>CE = EE+CS<br />\n<br />\nCS = Computer Science<br />\n<br />\n絕大部分香港做緊既IT = Information System<br />\n<br />\n外國IT公司做緊既IT = CS/CE<br />\n<br />\n外國非IT公司做緊既IT = Information System</blockquote><br />\n咁即係香港做IT好搵啲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然不是。<br />\n<br />\nInformation System (IS) 的地位，同一間公司中其他的 business function (Accounting, Finance, Operations Management, Human Resources Management) 的地位一樣，只係support business 的運作，點會好搵 ?</blockquote><br />\n人事部正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}